text: Park Soo-yun (born 27 November 1974) is a South Korean badminton player. She competed in women's doubles at the 1996 Summer Olympics in Atlanta. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of South Korea Category:Badminton players at the 1996 Summer Olympics
